during a recent tour in the southwest, his
sonic brush is a bit heavier and the mood
a little darker this go-around.

alt-country band the Gilded Splinters,
Buckley moved from Boston to Austin
in 2011. Ranging from rough to raw to
rueful, Buckley’s sound caught ears and
landed him residencies at the White
Horse, Blackheart, Hotel Vegas, and
Hole in the Wall, gigs at Nashville’s famed
Bluebird Cafe, and airplay from KUT to
